titolo = "SIEM - Level 3"
descrizione = "Full-scale security intelligence with real-time threat hunting and predictive analytics. From a security standpoint, Level 3 shifts your posture from reactive to proactive — instead of waiting for alerts, your team actively hunts for hidden threats already inside the network, catching attackers before they can cause serious damage."
